If there’s a summer vacation in your future filled with warm sandy beaches and plenty of swimming opportunities, you’re going to need a bathing suit that’s a blend of function, fashion and comfort. The following list of swim outfits include everything from cheeky string bikinis, fuller coverage one-pieces, fun patterned tankinis and cute rash guards that can protect your skin while you have fun in the sun. HuffPost may receive a share from purchases made via links on this page. Prices and availability are subject to change.Unless otherwise specified, all sizes in this post are listed in women’s.